  "id": "BIT-hubble-relay-2026-41520",
  "summary": "Cillium exposes sensitive information included in the cilium-bugtool debug archive",
  "details": "Cilium is a networking, observability, and security solution with an eBPF-based dataplane. Prior to versions 1.17.15, 1.18.9, and 1.19.3, the output of cilium-bugtool can contain sensitive data when the tool is run against Cilium deployments with WireGuard encryption enabled. This issue has been patched in versions 1.17.15, 1.18.9, and 1.19.3.",
